{"tid":1850226,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽！工作場所內，口罩係由僱主提供，並非僱員自備","createTime":"2020-01-29T12:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T06:17:06.000Z","uid":276716,"like":471,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3e132ee5d1491d83eacb52e7a2824b17469daa","tid":1850226,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"今日好多人撲口罩，又話某啲行業嘅人可以優先買。<br />\n<br />\n必須嚴正聲明，<span style=\"color: red;\">工作場所內提供口罩係僱主責任，唔係由僱員自備。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據《職業安全及健康條例》，僱主有責任提供安全工作環境。職業安全健康局出版嘅刊物亦提到，<span style=\"color: red;\">僱主必須備有足夠口罩供僱員使用。</span><br />\n參考<a href=\"http://www.oshc.org.hk/oshc_data/files/HotTopic/Workplace%20Influ%20leaflet%2009%20New.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oshc.org.hk%2Foshc_data%2Ffiles%2FHotTopic%2FWorkplace%2520Influ%2520leaflet%252009%2520New.pdf&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH4D442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=a6e06c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.oshc.org.hk/oshc_data/files/HotTopic/Workplace%20Influ%20leaflet%2009%20New.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果僱主要求你喺某個場所內工作，例如office，而不提供足夠口罩，佢有可能已經犯法。</span><br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況，你可以向勞工處舉報。下面係職安健投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/ld0001/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fld0001%2Ftc%2F&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH4D442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=a9a7e654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/ld0001/tc/</a><br />\n<br />\n記住，要撲口罩嘅係老闆，唔係打公仔。"},{"pid":"f1b85941d6e578c6053691ceffd101ebec92074d","tid":1850226,"uid":54833,"like":50,"dislike":9,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"老細叫你走！你搵定第份！"},{"pid":"f7b90e608da688e5ef54ff4349acc3e1f7949af5","tid":1850226,"uid":7807,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:19:09.000Z","msg":"公司係有每日兩個比我地，其他巴打真係可以同公司爭取下，不過，買唔到就真係買唔到，你老闆都係搵你人事部同事買⋯⋯⋯你人事部同事買到既話，其實你都有可能買到⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"02b54969029346cbd23c853edfc1f1fbf0b06